quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,82,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Alla …ìe jokki sari'a Makko on, hara …ìe jillaali e gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe ngal sirku, hino woodani hoolaare kam…ìa tan, ko kam…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe fewniri laawol peewal."
  6,83,"On hujja ar…óo ka Daalol Allah : (Ko honnde e feddeeji …óin …ói…ói …ìuri hanndude e dee∆¥ere?) mo Ibraahiima foolirnoo yim…ìe mun …ìen, ko hujja Amen mo Men Ye…ói mo e dow yim…ìe makko …ìen. Me…óen ∆Åamtira darja on mo Men Muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen aduna e laakara. Pellet, Joomi maa…óa an Nulaa…óo, ko √ëee√±o e tagu Makko ngun e toppitagol Mo ngol, Anndu…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  6,84,"Men Arsiki Ibraahiima …ìi…ó…óo wi'etee…óo Ishaaqa e taaniraawo wi'etee…óo Yaaquuba, Men Fewni …ìe …ói…óo kala e laawol focciingol. Men Fewni Nuuhu ado ma…ì…ìe, Men Fewni e jurriiya Nuuhu on Daawuuda e …ìi…ó…óo makko on Sulaymaana, e Ayyuuba e Yuusufa e Muusa e neene-gooto makko on Haaruuna (yo …ìe his). Ko wano Men Yo…ìitiri nii …ìee Annbaa…ìe e mo∆¥∆¥ere ma…ì…ìe nden, Men Yo…ìitirta kala mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe."
  6,85,"Men Fewni kadi Zakariyaa e Yahyaa e Iisaa …ìi…ó…óo Maryama on e Ilyaasa (yo …ìe his). ∆Åen Annabaa…ìe …óon kala ko jeyaa…ìe e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìe Alla Su…ìii Wa…ói Nulaa…ìe."
  6,86,"Men Fewni kadi Ismaa'iila e Alyasa'a e Luutu, …ìen Annabaa…ìe …óon fow wonndude e Annabiijo Muhammadu (yo o his), Men ∆Åurnii …ìe e Winndere nden."
  6,87,"Men Fewni kadi …ìen …ìe Men Muuyi e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, e yoga e …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe, e yoga e musi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe. Men Su…ìii …ìe, Men Fewni …ìe e laawol focciingol ; ngol woni laawol tawhiidi."
  6,88,"Ngal peewal ngal …ìe hawrondiri, ko Alla Hawrindini …ìe e maggal ; himo Fewna on Mo O Muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Sinno …ìe kafiduno e Alla go…ó…óum goo, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen bonayno ; tawde sirku bonnay golle mo∆¥∆¥e."
  6,89,"Ko …ìen Annabaa…ìe …óon woni …ìe men Okki Defte, e √ëen∆¥al, e Annabaaku. Si yim…ìe maa …ìen yeddii ko Men Addani …ìe kon e …óin tati, gom…óii Men Hebilanii …ói yim…ìe goo …ìe laataaki yeddoo…ìe …ói ; …ìen ko gom…óim…ìe ja…ìoo…ìe …ói, ko …ìen woni feru…ìe …ìen e yim…ìe madiina …ìen jokkir…ìe …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere haa √ëalnde njo…ìdi diina."
  6,90,"∆Åe Annabaa…ìe jantodaa…ìe e baabiraa…ìe mun e …ìi…ó…ìe mun e musi…ó…ìe mun, ko …ìen woni feewir…ìe goonga : jokkito …ìe √±emtinaa …ìe. Maakan yim…ìe maa …ìen an Nulaa…óo : "Mi …óa…ì…ìiraa on yottingol ndee Qur'aanaare njo…ìdi", Qur'aanaare nden wonaali si wanaa waaju Winndere nden ; immorde e yim…ìe e jinna, fii ko fewna …ìe e laawol goonga."